data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom split level home, convenient to downtown Norfolk, I-264 & I-64.The main level features an open concept, blending the L/R & D/R. Lots of natural light thanks to the large windows that overlook the front yard. A few steps up from the main level, you’ll find the private sleeping quarters & Steps down from the main level you’ll find an extra room, Ideal for overnight guests or extended family. Outside, this property boasts a beautiful landscaped yard. A large backyard to include a patio for your outdoor entertainment.  ***Seller to assist Buyer with 1.5% in closing cost assistance with an acceptable offer.***  ****203K loan option available with a preferred lender, in addition, to a $1800.00 lender credit.****
